This is a map with 6 hidden teleports behind boxes that break. It has two long skinny basements and two long wall slots, but best is the two launchers that literally launch people to the other side of the map. Plus, two of the portals lead up to the sky sniping spots. but no worry to get down all you need to do is jump into the water. the map made some of my members lag so i changed the water to "cheap" water but if i get requests for "expensive" water i will upload that.

This is my first map, Im happy to read your comments :D

Installation: 1. Once you have downloaded the map, you want to extract or unzip the map. 

2. The next step would be going to your SteamApps file which is located at: C:\Program Files\Steam

3. Now that your in your SteamApps file, go into your account name.

4. Now go into your Counter Strike:Source file.

5. Now go into your cstrike file. 

6. Now have your cstrike file and the file with your map both on the screen. 

7. Now your going to drag the files for your map onto the cstrike folder. 

8. It will ask you if you want to replace or copy the folders. Hit yes to all.

9. When it finishes, your map has been installed.

This map was designed for use in gungame. It has the layout of a small maze, with a fountain in the middle of the map, which also has ladders above it, which allow players to access the upper level to have an advantage over the enemy. I have also included two portals in the map which allow players to quickly access the other side of the map.

I hope you like it!

This is a remake of Stryker's fy_funtimes. The biggest change from funtimes is the bottom area underneath the generic funtimes layout. Spawns are significantly lower in order to prevent spawn camping with access to both the "normal" level and the bottom level. Rather than ladders for access to the tops of the 4 main boxes, I used stairs. Also, next to those stairs there is access to the bottom area. On the sides of the map where the typical blocking wall is, there is a breakable box to make it hard for people to sit behind the whole time. 

If you upload it to your server or modify it please post here or pm me! I'd love to hear about it.
